\/p>\n<h2 id=\"fees-category-and-option\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Fees_Category_and_option\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81315456\"><\/a>Fees Category and option<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To learn more about fees and student financial services visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.usherbrooke.ca\/international\/en\/international-students\/admission\/\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-and-when-to-pay-fees\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_and_When_to_Pay_Fees\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81315457\"><\/a>How and When to Pay Fees<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>How to make payments through online banking <\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Log into your bank\u2019s online system.<\/li>\n<li>Add the Universit\u00e9 de Sherbrooke as a payee on your bill payment profile<\/li>\n<li>Enter your account details<\/li>\n<li>Note that it may take up to 10 business days for your payment to process.<\/li>\n<li>Your university fees consist of Tuition and others Costs based on your faculty and degree.<\/li>\n<li>To complete registration, you\u2019ll need to pay your fees ahead of\u00a0your Faculty\u2019s registration deadlines.<\/li>\n<li>To pay your Universit\u00e9 de Sherbrooke\u2019s faculty fees click <a href=\"https:\/\/www.usherbrooke.ca\/international\/en\/international-students\/admission\/\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"registration-time-limit-universite-de-sherbrooke-fees\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Registration_time_limit_Universite_de_Sherbrooke_Fees\"><\/span>\u00a0<a name=\"_Toc81315458\"><\/a>Registration time limit| Universit\u00e9 de Sherbrooke Fees<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>You will need to pay your tuition, incidental and ancillary fees by the date fixed or arrange for a payment deferral if you\u2019ll be receiving the government&#8217;s financial aid. Click <a href=\"https:\/\/www.usherbrooke.ca\/international\/en\/international-students\/admission\/\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> to view Deadlines.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-pay-universite-de-sherbrooke-fees\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Pay_Universite_de_Sherbrooke_Fees\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81315459\"><\/a>How to Pay| Universit\u00e9 de Sherbrooke Fees<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Find out more supplementary information about Registration Steps and Deadlines, including directions on paying your Fees and Requesting a Tuition Fee Deferral <a href=\"https:\/\/www.usherbrooke.ca\/international\/en\/international-students\/admission\/\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>For more information about Universit\u00e9 de Sherbrooke, Academic and Other fees visit<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Kindly check <a href=\"https:\/\/www.usherbrooke.ca\/international\/en\/international-students\/admission\/\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> for more information about how to enroll, pay fees, and more.<\/p>\n<p>For more information visit the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.usherbrooke.ca\/international\/en\/international-students\/admission\/\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Student Financial Assistance<\/a> for guidance, information, tools, and services to help you meet your financial needs or complaints.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; The University of British Columbia<br \/>\n<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Universit\u00e9 de Sherbrooke Fees for International Students 2024 \u2013Fees &amp; Costs. University Fees. Incidental and Ancillary Fees, faculty,&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1808,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":fals